PN,37901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776859866
OL,3,CFormer patients of doctor urge
OL,4,Ccriminal investigation to be expanded
OL,6,FThe alleged victims of a former Derby
OL,7,Fdoctor are calling for the criminal
OL,8,Finvestigation into his medical
OL,9,Fpractices to be expanded, as they call
OL,10,Ffor "justice" following his death.
OL,12,FDaniel Hay, 61, from near Alfreton,
OL,13,Fdied earlier this month in hospital of
OL,14,Fnatural causes, while at the centre of
OL,15,Fa three-year criminal investigation
OL,16,Finto his medical practices involving
OL,17,Fdozens of women.
OL,26,@rD@EOUrD@MO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776859866
OL,3,CFormer patients of doctor urge
OL,4,Ccriminal investigation to be expanded
OL,6,FA report released last year by Hay's
OL,7,Fformer employer, the University
OL,8,FHospitals of Derby and Burton NHS
OL,9,FFoundation Trust (UHDB), described him
OL,10,Fas a "risk-taking" doctor, who harmed
OL,11,Fdozens of women by performing
OL,12,Fsurgeries without consent that went
OL,13,Fvirtually unchecked by hospital bosses.
OL,15,FThe report looked into his conduct in
OL,16,F383 cases between 2015 to 2018, and
OL,17,Fhas since been expanded to include
OL,18,F2012-2015, but some alleged victims
OL,19,Fwant the investigation to start as far
OL,20,Fback as 2001.
OL,26,@rD@FOUrD@RO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776859866
OL,3,CFormer patients of doctor urge
OL,4,Ccriminal investigation to be expanded
OL,6,FThe report found "major" concerns of
OL,7,Fharm to 48 women and "some" concerns
OL,8,Fof harm to 68 women, although it did
OL,9,Fnot provide a definition of "concerns
OL,10,Fof harm".
OL,12,FHay was interviewed under caution on
OL,13,Fnumerous occasions from late March
OL,14,F2025, but was never charged with a
OL,15,Fcrime.
OL,17,FCriminal investigations into six out
OL,18,Fof 36 cases were dropped by Derbyshire
OL,19,FPolice in January this year, due to a
OL,20,Flack of evidence.
OL,26,@nD@ROUnD@XO]oD@VOUoD@[O]qD@]OUrD@HO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776859866
OL,3,CFormer patients of doctor urge
OL,4,Ccriminal investigation to be expanded
OL,6,FPolice have confirmed there was no
OL,7,Fdate limit to its investigations but
OL,8,Fthat they were restricted to purely
OL,9,Ffocus on Hay, with no other person
OL,10,Finterviewed or within scope.
OL,12,FHay worked across the "mid-Trent" area
OL,13,Fbetween 1996-2001 at Queen's Medical
OL,14,FCentre and City Hospital in
OL,15,FNottingham, King's Mill Hospital in
OL,16,FMansfield, what was Derby City General
OL,17,FHospital and Chesterfield Royal
OL,18,FHospital.
OL,26,@tD@WOUtD@aO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776859866
OL,3,CFormer patients of doctor urge
OL,4,Ccriminal investigation to be expanded
OL,6,FFrom 2001 to 2005, he worked at
OL,7,FChesterfield Royal and from 2006 until
OL,8,F2020 at Royal Derby Hospital, along
OL,9,Fwith teaching roles at the University
OL,10,Fof Nottingham and Sheffield Medical
OL,11,FSchool.
OL,13,F"Shouldn't mean we don't get justice"
OL,14,FPauline Hill, who now lives in
OL,15,FLeicestershire, was treated by Hay in
OL,16,F2001, while he was working at
OL,17,FChesterfield Royal Hospital.
OL,19,FShe said: "I keep fighting for older
OL,20,Fcases to be taken into consideration,
OL,21,Fbut it has still been ignored.
OL,26,@{D@KOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776859866
OL,3,CFormer patients of doctor urge
OL,4,Ccriminal investigation to be expanded
OL,6,F"The problem is, will the real number
OL,7,Fever be known? As many old cases will
OL,8,Finclude many that have died.
OL,10,F"Some are too fearful of reigniting
OL,11,Fold experiences and in this age range
OL,12,Fa lot of women won't speak of such
OL,13,Fthings as it is far too embarrassing
OL,14,Ffor them.
OL,16,F"The GMC were aware of Hay in 2003.
OL,17,FWhilst Hay is now gone, that shouldn't
OL,18,Fmean we don't get justice so we can
OL,19,Fmove on."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUxD@AOU{D@IO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776859866
OL,3,CFormer patients of doctor urge
OL,4,Ccriminal investigation to be expanded
OL,6,FMrs Hill had her request for a GMC
OL,7,Finvestigation rejected in 2005, and a
OL,8,Frequest for a review was also rejected
OL,9,Fin 2007.
OL,11,FLast October's NHS report into Hay
OL,12,Freferenced this case, saying: "There
OL,13,Fis some evidence that as soon as he
OL,14,Farrived in post (at Royal Derby, in
OL,15,F2006), he was concerned about a GMC
OL,16,Finvestigation over a patient's
OL,17,Ftreatment from his previous position
OL,18,Fat Chesterfield Hospital."
OL,20,F"I thought I was going to die"
OL,26,@tD@_OUzD@ZO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776859866
OL,3,CFormer patients of doctor urge
OL,4,Ccriminal investigation to be expanded
OL,6,FSteph Blood, from Nottingham, had an
OL,7,Fabdominal hysterectomy performed by
OL,8,FHay at QMC in 2001, leading to a
OL,9,F#33,000 compensation payout from the
OL,10,FNottingham hospitals trust, after it
OL,11,Fadmitted "breach of duty".
OL,13,FA further former patient, living in
OL,14,FDerbyshire, who did not wish to be
OL,15,Fnamed, had a hysterectomy performed by
OL,16,FHay in 2007 at Royal Derby Hospital.
OL,18,FShe said: "I thought I was going to
OL,19,Fdie. I called the Vicar to give
OL,20,Fcommunion.
OL,26,@sD@JOUsD@YO]zD@KOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776859866
OL,3,CFormer patients of doctor urge
OL,4,Ccriminal investigation to be expanded
OL,6,F"You don't want anyone to suffer but I
OL,7,Fwanted him to be punished for what he
OL,8,Fdid and to reflect on what he has done
OL,9,Fwrong to us all.
OL,11,F"The trust and all the other trusts
OL,12,Fneed to be honest about what they
OL,13,Fknew. They all need to be honest."
OL,15,FMelissa Newbold, aged 40, from Derby,
OL,16,Fhad a womb ablation (involving the
OL,17,Flining of the uterus) followed by a
OL,18,Fhysterectomy performed by Hay from
OL,19,F2013 to 2014.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776859866
OL,3,CFormer patients of doctor urge
OL,4,Ccriminal investigation to be expanded
OL,6,FShe said: "It was a bit of a shock. I
OL,7,Fdo feel sad about it, I don't want
OL,8,Fanybody to die, but we are also now
OL,9,Fback to being in limbo."
OL,11,FHannah Green, 36, from Littleover, had
OL,12,Flaparoscopies performed by Hay in 2016
OL,13,Fand 2017, without her consent.
OL,15,FHer case was one of the six dropped by
OL,16,Fthe police in January, which she
OL,17,Fclaims was linked to the lack of
OL,18,Fmedical experts available to assess
OL,19,Fand provide evidence to support a
OL,20,Fcriminal charge.
OL,26,@nD@KOUqD@XO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776859866
OL,3,CFormer patients of doctor urge
OL,4,Ccriminal investigation to be expanded
OL,6,FShe said she and the other five women
OL,7,Fwho had their cases dropped have
OL,8,Fappealed that decision.
OL,10,FMs Green said: "I was quite
OL,11,Fflabbergasted when I found out. It
OL,12,Fcame as quite a shock.
OL,14,F"Daniel Hay ought to have died in
OL,15,Fprison, but there is still a job to do
OL,16,Fto investigate everybody else.
OL,18,F"The police need to look into how this
OL,19,Fwas allowed to happen."
OL,26,@rD@POUvD@AOUzD@AOU{D@WO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776859866
OL,3,CFormer patients of doctor urge
OL,4,Ccriminal investigation to be expanded
OL,6,FA Chesterfield Royal Hospital
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "Daniel Hay worked
OL,8,Fat Chesterfield Royal Hospital NHS
OL,9,FFoundation Trust between 1996 and
OL,10,F2005, and we take any concerns about
OL,11,Fpatient safety extremely seriously.
OL,13,F"Matters relating to wider
OL,14,Finvestigations into an individual
OL,15,Fclinician's practice are led by the
OL,16,Fappropriate national bodies, and the
OL,17,Ftrust will continue to cooperate fully
OL,18,Fwith any external reviews or
OL,19,Fenquiries."
OL,26,@oD@TOUuD@AOU{D@KO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776859866
OL,3,CFormer patients of doctor urge
OL,4,Ccriminal investigation to be expanded
OL,6,FDr Gis Robinson, executive chief
OL,7,Fmedical officer at UHDB, said: "We
OL,8,Freiterate our unreserved apologies to
OL,9,Fthe women who received care that fell
OL,10,Fbelow the standards they should have
OL,11,Fbeen able to rely on.
OL,13,F"The published independent reports
OL,14,Fwere wideranging, involving staff as
OL,15,Fwell as reviews of clinical records to
OL,16,Fbuild a full understanding of what
OL,17,Fhappened and where care fell short.
OL,26,@oD@`OUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G13/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37914
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776859866
OL,3,CFormer patients of doctor urge
OL,4,Ccriminal investigation to be expanded
OL,6,F"We made changes to the way the
OL,7,Forganisation works on the back of the
OL,8,Ffindings, including how consent is
OL,9,Fagreed and recorded, how clinical work
OL,10,Fis overseen, and how women are
OL,11,Freviewed after procedures.
OL,13,F"A further review ` called 'phase 2' `
OL,14,Fis already underway of a defined group
OL,15,Fof women who underwent major surgery
OL,16,Fby Mr Hay before 2015, and our focus
OL,17,Fremains on supporting those affected,
OL,18,Fbeing open and transparent, and
OL,19,Fensuring any further learning is acted
OL,20,Fupon."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU|D@FO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G14/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37915
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776859866
OL,3,CFormer patients of doctor urge
OL,4,Ccriminal investigation to be expanded
OL,6,F"The investigation into these
OL,7,Fallegations is complex"
OL,9,FDerbyshire Police said it is not the
OL,10,Fcase that the Lucy Letby case, or any
OL,11,Fother case, has had an impact on
OL,12,Favailable experts for the Daniel Hay
OL,13,Finvestigation, but acknowledged there
OL,14,Fare limited numbers of gynaecological
OL,15,Fmedical experts that can undertake
OL,16,Fcriminal matters.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G15/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37916
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776859866
OL,3,CFormer patients of doctor urge
OL,4,Ccriminal investigation to be expanded
OL,6,FThe force spokesperson said: "We
OL,7,Funderstand that Daniel Hay's death
OL,8,Fwill have had a significant impact on
OL,9,Fall of those involved in this
OL,10,Finvestigation.
OL,12,F"The investigation into these
OL,13,Fallegations is complex, involving
OL,14,Flarge amounts of material and
OL,15,Findependent specialist medical
OL,16,Fprofessionals being consulted.
OL,26,@nD@^OUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G16/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37917
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776859866
OL,3,CFormer patients of doctor urge
OL,4,Ccriminal investigation to be expanded
OL,6,F"While this has meant that enquiries
OL,7,Fhave taken a significant length of
OL,8,Ftime it is important that these
OL,9,Fenquiries are undertaken in a diligent
OL,10,Fand comprehensive way.
OL,12,F"Following this latest development a
OL,13,Freview is being undertaken into what
OL,14,Fthe next steps are for the
OL,15,Finvestigation, and we will continue to
OL,16,Fkeep those involved updated."
OL,18,FThe Nottingham University Hospital NHS
OL,19,FTrust was approached for comment but
OL,20,Fhas not yet responded.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@]O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G17/18
